id: pmc-55cp
title: Fix changelog export format validation and metadata
description: "Codex review on pm-cli PR #99 found two pm-changelog package defects in the managed 2026.6.2 extension: changelog export accepts unsupported --format values by falling through to markdown, and registerExporter lacks metadata for --format/--output/--since/etc. Duplicate check: pm search \"changelog export format registerExporter metadata\" found no open direct duplicate."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: agent-ux,contracts,exporter,extension
